Package: rivermile
Type: Package
Title: Assign River Miles to Monitoring Locations
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Maddee Wiggins
Maintainer: Maddee Wiggins <mrubenson@flowwest.com>
Description: This package provides tools for working with river mile data, allowing users to find the nearest river mile for spatial points along water bodies.
